---
title: Beijing Style Chicken Breast and Pak Choi Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Beijing Style Chicken Breast and Pak Choi Stir-Fry in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R11_W09_UK_QR13723-17_MAIN_low-d99606fd.jpg
